DECLARE @bSplit NVARCHAR(MAX) = N'Jotform-style premium 2-column split layout: image / branded hero on the LEFT (~40-50% width with title + subtitle overlay), form fields on the RIGHT. The most-requested "premium" look users ask for in the AI Form Creator modal.

🛑 MANDATORY RULE — every field in `fields[]` MUST appear as `{{field:KEY}}` somewhere in customHtml. If you list 5 fields but only place 3 placeholders, 2 fields render INVISIBLE at runtime (the previous AI Form Creator bug — form 281 showed right column blank because AI emitted customHtml without placeholders). Validator [PRESERVE-001] / [SPLIT-001] rejects this.

